short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Toggle to View Documentation in Full Width

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension adds a button to MS Docs pages to support collapsing and expanding the sidebar.  It also auto-expands down the table of contents on documentation articles so you can see the complete list of sections.
